briefTitle: A Study to Compare SB16 (Proposed Denosumab Biosimilar) to Prolia® in Postmenopausal Women With Osteoporosis
officialTitle: A Phase III, Randomised, Double-blind, Multicentre Clinical Study to Compare the Efficacy, Safety, Pharmacokinetics, Pharmacodynamics, and Immunogenicity Between SB16 (Proposed Denosumab Biosimilar) and Prolia® in Postmenopausal Women With Osteoporosis
summary: This is a randomised, double-blind, multicentre study to evaluate the efficacy, safety, PK, PD, and immunogenicity of SB16 compared to Prolia® in postmenopausal women with osteoporosis.

primaryOutcome.measure: Percent Change From Baseline in Lumbar Spine BMD at Month 12
